State of North Carolina
v.
Corey L. Hendricks-Bey No. 238P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2016 Corey L. Hendricks, for Hendricks, Corey L. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 20th of June 2016 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th of August 2016."
